"""
LexRAG: Multi-Agent Legal Document Q&A System
==============================================
Author : Harshvardhan Tiwari
Stack  : LangChain · Ollama (Mistral-7B) · ChromaDB · HuggingFace Embeddings · RAGAS

Architecture
------------
  PDF Ingestion → Semantic Chunking → ChromaDB Vector Store
       ↓
